* About

  This is a unit test for MacRuby which based on Ruby 1.9.2.

* Test

  Execute the unit test following commands.
  $ rake

  Test results are stored in "result" directory.

* Bootstraptest

  Execute the unit test following commands.
  $ cd bootstraptest
  $ ./runner.rb

* Attention

  1. MacRuby zombie processes might be generated after running the tests.
     To kill all MacRuby process:
     $ rake kill

  2. Your "~/.gemrc" and "~/.gem" files might be changed after running the tests.
     Please back up beforehand.

  3. Now, it takes around 1 hour to run the tests.
